475
00:32:15,017 --> 00:32:18,020
Family farms can make a living again.


476
00:32:18,020 --> 00:32:23,442
That's what 2050 could look like, for all
of us, if we radically turn the tide now.

477
00:32:23,650 --> 00:32:27,654
And I don’t know about you,
