00:33:52,220 --> 00:33:56,620
So if we reduce food waste and if we get
more proteins from plants and from plant-based

499
00:33:56,620 --> 00:34:00,038
meat and dairy, we could free up so much land.


500
00:34:00,600 --> 00:34:05,080
Not only could we feed everyone, but we
could return huge tracts of less productive land

501
00:34:05,080 --> 00:34:08,580
to nature and let them go wild again!


502
00:34:08,580 --> 00:34:11,599
So that’s the better
story when it comes to Food.

503
00:34:11,599 --> 00:34:17,014
A new story is also emerging for consumption
and production, the other topic we talked about.

504
00:34:17,399 --> 00:34:22,490
Well, in many ways, this new story is full
of common sense and wisdom from the past.

505
00:34:22,490 --> 00:34:26,648
It tells us something
we all know deep down inside.

506
00:34:27,020 --> 00:34:32,080
What really makes us happy
