00:37:49,059 --> 00:37:55,023
And it also builds community, the very thing
that has been proven to make us happier in life!

558
00:37:55,649 --> 00:37:58,230
You know, that to me is like the better story.


559
00:37:58,230 --> 00:37:59,230
We can relax.


560
00:37:59,230 --> 00:38:04,032
We spend less money and yet we have
access to what we need when we need it.

